      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "Forty participants were selected after being prescreened using the WOMAC scores.  The total WOMAC score on day zero (pretreatment) showed a mean (± standard deviation [SD]) of 67.8 (±8.8) for the group assigned to the placebo treatment and 62.5 (±5.31) for the group assigned to the BRC treatment."
